--   Tables   : 4   (greeting_templates, recipients, greeting_events, app_config)
--   Columns  : 43  total across all tables
--   Indexes  : 17  (14 regular + 1 partial unique + 2 partial composite)
--   FK refs  : 2   (greeting_events → greeting_templates, → recipients)
--   CHK const: 11  across all tables
--   UNIQUE   : 3   (template_key, config_key, single_default)
--   Triggers : 3   (updated_at on greeting_templates, recipients, app_config)
--   Views    : 4   (v_active_greeting_templates, v_default_recipient,
--                   v_greeting_event_summary, v_workflow_statistics)
--   Seed rows: 15  (4 templates + 2 recipients + 8 app_config + 1 greeting_event)
--
-- Business rules fully covered by schema elements:
--   BR-001 (default args)  → resolution_strategy = 'DEFAULT_USED', workflow_id = 'WF-001'
--   BR-002 (stdout output) → output_channel DEFAULT 'STDOUT', CHECK constraint
--   BR-004 (null args)     → requested_recipient nullable column
--   BR-005 (empty args)    → args_count = 0 seed, CHECK args_count >= 0
--   BR-006 (first arg)     → single requested_recipient column
--   BR-008 (null fallback) → resolution_strategy = 'DEFAULT_USED'
--   BR-009 (blank fallback)→ resolution_strategy = 'BLANK_FALLBACK', consistency CHECK
--   BR-010 (trim)          → chk_recipients_name_not_blank, column comment
--   BR-011 (format)        → generated_greeting NOT NULL, FK to template
--   BR-012 (template)      → seed row 'Hello %s', chk value has placeholder
--   BR-013 (default recip) → seed row 'World' with is_default=TRUE
--   BR-014 (one placeholder)→ chk_placeholder_count = 1, chk value has %s
